name: Hartog Jacobs
overview:
Hartog Jacobs LLC is a full-service business consulting firm based in Cedarhurst, NY. Founded in 2011, the information technology and management consultancy makes it easier for enterprise clients and entrepreneurs to manage their businesses. Our team of skilled consultants has helped countless businesses examine their business practices and create strategies that deliver noticeable cost-savings and rapid financial growth.

Services that Hartog Jacobs offers includes business plan development, business strategy, web development, search engine optimization, e-mail management service, phone setup services, cellular services, business credit services, digital marketing solutions, supplies, media campaigns, online reputation services, technical support, and crisis management services.

Whether a business is a startup or a large enterprise client, Hartog Jacobs has solutions custom tailored to match each individual client’s needs.
